      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 model is a distilled version of a 19-billion parameter model optimized for FP8 (8-bit floating point) precision. This reduces memory footprint and accelerates inference while maintaining accuracy suitable for most API use cases. Key features include lower latency compared to FP16 variants and compatibility with modern GPU architectures that support FP8 operations."
