        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "API Integration Steps for LTX-2 19B Distilled FP8 api a"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the model, start by setting up a RESTful API endpoint using frameworks like FastAPI or Flask. Ensure your server has CUDA-enabled GPUs with FP8 support. Configure the model loader to use FP8 weights, and implement authentication via API keys. Example endpoint structure: POST /v1/inference with JSON payload containing input text and parameters like max_tokens and temperature."
